                        tortor, sed fermentum nunc. Pellentesque fermentum nunc feugiat maximus finibus. Donec justo
                        sem, dignissim eu pretium ut, pellentesque at ante.</p>
                    <p>Cras commodo dapibus sem, ut volutpat odio aliquam vel. Mauris molestie blandit eros vel
                        placerat. Curabitur in diam id urna cursus cursus in at quam. Fusce iaculis, odio at tincidunt
                        aliquam, sem urna fringilla ligula, nec sollicitudin odio eros eget purus. Donec at diam
                        aliquet, iaculis nibh quis, mattis ipsum.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>100% organic fresh vegetables</li>
                        <li>Non-GMO products</li>
                        <li>Locally grown and harvested</li>
                        <li>Rich in vitamins and minerals</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-pane @(ActiveTabIndex == 1 ? "active" : "")">
                    <table class="product-attributes">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Weight</th>
                                <td>250g, 500g, 1kg, 5kg</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Origin</th>
                                <td>Local Farm</td>
